REGULATORY AND FRAMEWORK CONTENT
---------------------------------
Guidance within this tool relating to ITIL 4, DORA (EU Regulation
2022/2554), FCA Operational Resilience, UK GDPR, SAFe, DORA metrics
and related frameworks is informational only.

It is NOT legal advice, compliance advice, or a substitute for
professional guidance. Framework definitions, regulatory thresholds
and obligations change over time. Always verify requirements against
authoritative sources (AXELOS/PeopleCert, dora.dev, FCA Handbook,
EBA, ICO) and engage your compliance team or legal counsel for
decisions specific to your organisation and regulated activities.

The author provides no warranty as to the accuracy, completeness or
currency of any regulatory, framework or methodology guidance shown.

