DATA AND PRIVACY
----------------
This tool operates entirely in your browser (local-first). No data
is transmitted to any server by the tool itself. All release data,
defect records and settings are stored in your browser's localStorage.
The author has no access to any data entered into this tool.

Third-party fonts are loaded from Google Fonts (fonts.googleapis.com).
Consult your organisation's acceptable use policy regarding external
font loading if this is a concern.

